---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Kyxel Security Privacy Policy"
  description="Understand how Kyxel Security collects, stores and processes data."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#030417] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300">Last updated: November 2025</p>
      <p class="text-slate-300">
        Kyxel Security collects only the data required to deliver our service: account details, telemetry sent by your agents, and product analytics.
        We never sell data to third parties. Telemetry is encrypted in transit and at rest.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">Data we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-slate-300 space-y-2">
        <li>Account & billing information provided by you.</li>
        <li>Server telemetry and metadata submitted by your Kyxel agents.</li>
        <li>Product usage metrics collected to improve the dashboard experience.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8">Your rights</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300">
        You can request deletion or export of your data anytime by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@kyxel.studio" class="text-cyan-300 underline">privacy@kyxel.studio</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

